Class FileHandler

Object
FileHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
IFileHandler
public class FileHandler extends Object implements IFileHandler
Handles reading from and writing to CSV files. This class implements the IFileHandler interface and interacts with the IDataRepo abstraction rather than the concrete DataRepo implementation. This design adheres to the Dependency Inversion Principle (DIP), allowing UIs and controllers to depend on abstractions instead of concrete classes.
